{"tid":2297402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九龍草地滾球會逾百人活動 會員場邊聚集除罩飲食","createTime":"2020-11-23T09:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T09:24:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e16db09c16aa3ad9d32b81f6b59a62bac6e0c3b9","tid":2297402,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:03:15.000Z","msg":"本港武漢肺炎恐爆發第四波疫情，然而有市民上周五卻發現有草地滾球會舉辦活動，其間超過百人聚集，記者隨後到場視察，更目擊有會員在場邊除罩飲食，令人有播疫隱憂。<br />\n<br />\n現場是位於尖沙嘴柯士甸道的九龍草地滾球會，翻查資料該會成立於1900年，是香港首個草地滾球組織，可謂歷史悠久，而上周五該會舉行活動，慶祝成立120周年。有市民當日午開始便發現該會草地有大批人士聚集舉行活動，人數超過百人，質疑「點解冇限聚令呢」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201123/MBJZ4XSPXZDSFHA4YWKK2XPFJQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201123%2FMBJZ4XSPXZDSFHA4YWKK2XPFJQ%2F&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=60fee1a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201123%2FMBJZ4XSPXZDSFHA4YWKK2XPFJQ%2F&h=7e31cbc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201123/MBJZ4XSPXZDSFHA4YWKK2XPFJQ/</a>"},{"pid":"da9806a973a02238a76045412e296464b138ed66","tid":2297402,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:06:18.000Z","msg":"又係廢老活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34260e5c624a4070fad7acdcb1f10917ca4c80b","tid":2297402,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:07:18.000Z","msg":"廢老快啲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14a8fa4a781221cccf0f124f2e2e77b51787cfb","tid":2297402,"uid":320978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T09:11:13.000Z","msg":"會唔會有 碌嘢群組 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dcd0ecfea6dbbea9587d7332869d429ea949fa","tid":2297402,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"